            ]
        }, 
        {
            "body": "<p>Often the best way to spread fear and misery is to kill a beloved member of a community. This group of bugbears wishes to demoralize a town prior to a larger invasion, and is sneaking in to kill a respected council member.</p>", 
            "name": "Bugbear Murder Gang", 
            "url": "pfsrd://Monster Codex/Rules/Bugbears/Encounters/Bugbear Murder Gang", 
